{"tid":1535160,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[半集中討論] 最近我地嘅行動同輿論都俾人撳住黎打","createTime":"2019-09-03T09:00:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T10:11:11.000Z","uid":217242,"like":15,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"e31a4cb4cedae432ed2b0e64438c2d1c5285de6e","tid":1535160,"uid":217242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T09:00:52.000Z","msg":"事實係我地其實一直輸緊<br />\n不過差在未去到輸得一敗塗地<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n死嘅死 傷嘅傷 捉嘅捉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有好多野其實要檢討改善<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">我好希望大家可以俾d耐性睇下</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n首先係點解藍屍FB啲片會咁多like？！<br />\n點解仲有咁多人身處平行時空<br />\n唔係想帶風向 <br />\n只不過我有時刻留意對家一舉一動<br />\n<br />\n呢兩個月黎佢見證住佢地好多片<br />\n都係由幾千去到依家勁多views同like<br />\n可以話係同我地媒體陣營不相伯仲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你地可以上facebook打<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">HKG報 幫港出聲 紫荊雜誌 港人講地 等等</span></strong></span><br />\n事實證明其實有好大部份人係支持政府同警察<br />\n係呢個經濟社會 人數趨勢亦可能會越來越多 <br />\n而我地亦係面對住不分秋色嘅輿論壓力<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>無錯個班人我地係可以完全無視</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但我認為大家應該走出同溫層望下對家做緊乜嘢動作 </span></span><br />\n兼且儘量避免一班身處平衡時空嘅所謂中立人士港豬受佢地影響變為藍絲<br />\n你可能會話 <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">屌！個班人係有良知就一早支持我地啦 洗撚理佢感受服侍佢地咩！ <br />\n所謂知己知彼百戰百勝 除左行動輿論都要關注</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我明白大家嘅憤慨 但嬲之餘我地都要解決問題<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">因為要為之後選舉係輿論戰作準備</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係道德界線咁重嘅香港華人社會搞革命運動<br />\n我地本身已經係洩章 所以係呢一場持久戰上<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我地要盡量保持冷靜<br />\n減低自己出錯機會<br />\n加大敵人犯錯機率 </span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而點解我會咁講？<br />\n係因為呢2個月黎我訓覺係夢中所見<br />\n好多時正義之師有不完美需要改善的地方<br />\n例如語言行上對一d普通市民都欠缺禮貌<br />\n俾記者影住都忍唔到手推撞 <br />\n一開聲就鬧阿姐阿伯影相<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">而不合作運動本人係極不推薦再做</span></strong></span><br />\n因為針對性太低 而且對運動整體無好處<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">要記住選擇盲嘅人 你點逼佢睇都無用</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而呢d係事實發生咗 我唔係想怪大家同割蓆<br />\n不過我地做完要賽後檢討！儘量追求完美<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地要記住<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>身為紀律部隊嘅警察都控制唔到自己情緒<br />\n我地要更加表現出我地唔係所謂破壞份子</strong></span><br />\n我希望大家回望返初衷<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">我地嘅目的係針對政府同政權！<br />\n唔係普通市民同撐政府人士！</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我地可以憤怒 但唔好沖昏左頭腦<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">時刻保持理智 要以理服人為先 以力服人為後</span><br />\n我認為我地要時刻提醒周邊手足<br />\n同埋要訂立規矩去處理問題同衝突<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">第一步我地應該和平理性以禮相待</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n發現有人影相唔係影大頭 <br />\n或者可能言語上大家有誤會<br />\n我地其實可以好多時避免發生衝突 <br />\n善意提醒佢 或者禮貌叫佢del相<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>或者講聲唔好意思阻到你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">而第二步發現對方確實非常有問題</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔該大家！麻煩大家！唔好再婆婆媽媽對罵<br />\n我地有兩個方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一係冷靜處理 當佢傻人發噏風佢自然無癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一係立即圍埋一齊搞個燭光晚會<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">最好浪漫d唔好有光透到啦</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n專心跳舞摔角搞聚會之餘 最好唔好有相機出現<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>同埋搵侍應睇水留意有有惡犬衝黎咬人</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我只係發開口夢 現實出現純屬巧合<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">大家都可以一齊俾意見</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cp9kRRF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fcp9kRRF.jpg&h=eb348ba8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dc807997cf721ce92e7dec9d72b3048a34a6e75","tid":1535160,"uid":217242,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T09:01:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">關於戰術討論： </span></span><br />\n呢2個月黎實在承受住好大壓力<br />\n夢見幾次有手足被捉走而自己無能為力<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而每一次運動後都注定會損失手足<br />\n至今已經失去咗1000幾名同伴<br />\n不斷受住良心責備同內疚一人能力有限<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我其實無數次幻想係夢入邊拉人後退 嘗試救人<br />\n但每一次回望自己陣營 我都只能夠選擇放棄<br />\n好大原因在於我地一直輸心態<br />\n同埋每一次都有人大叫：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">防暴呀！速龍呀！走啊！！</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">我明白你係出於擔心先講呢句 <br />\n但係本身大家都已經係驚弓之鳥 <br />\n你知唔知咁樣做係十分影響軍心<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n從而令到前線人力不足陷入十分危險困境</span><br />\n俾人捉到最起碼十年 唔係得你一個驚<br />\n下次嘗試冷靜d 唔好雞飛狗走住<br />\n唔該可以嘗試嗌 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">冷靜D！救人呀！</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要記住你落得場就已經半隻腳踩咗入監倉<br />\n嘗試睇下有無機會救人 因為有排都未到你俾捉<br />\n要捉都捉最前邊個班先 <br />\n<br />\n同埋速龍黎捉人 好多時後邊班防暴會唔射住<br />\n調酒師同擲項選手可以嘗試用你方法<br />\n係步兵救人同時 防止對方綠兵支援推進<br />\n講真對方都係人 人多企定我唔信佢地唔驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望大家真係可以改變一下心態<br />\n每次個觀感好似未打就認輸咁<br />\n跟住返去又見到幾多幾多個人被捕<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">例子示範請睇返觀塘一役</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n救人進攻兼備 不過不適用於有水炮車情況下<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我只係發開口夢 現實出現純屬巧合<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">大家都可以一齊俾意見</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cp9kRRF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fcp9kRRF.jpg&h=eb348ba8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b38e0777d035c881b51e2693ce134989ee8f884a","tid":1535160,"uid":217242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T09:02:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cp9kRRF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fcp9kRRF.jpg&h=eb348ba8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"452d24b25606bf0edd0c7727c8a5804aa6ce4094","tid":1535160,"uid":217242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T09:03:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d6bae0f2f6bfface62ab412052dfd990aa42594","tid":1535160,"uid":217242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T09:03:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fdf4b9e44e15529f1a6ccfc0d218c4637c4bfc5","tid":1535160,"uid":217242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T09:03:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99eff0726453b954a657ba05cf697a7105276798","tid":1535160,"uid":217242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T09:03:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49bdc5d3d0f73580c57a591f9004486cddc3520a","tid":1535160,"uid":217242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T09:04:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b4048a36ba5b94b306f07e605cef735d69a732f","tid":1535160,"uid":217242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T09:05:03.000Z","msg":"<img src